@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!-- content
================================================== -->
<section class="s-content">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="column large-12">

            <section>

                <div class="s-content__media">
                    <img src="~/images/thumbs/about/about-1050.png"
                         srcset="~/images/thumbs/about/about-2100.png 2100w,
                                     ~/images/thumbs/about/about-1050.png 1050w,
                                     ~/images/thumbs/about/about-525.png 525w" sizes="(max-width: 2100px) 100vw, 2100px" alt="">
                </div> <!-- end s-content__media -->

                <div class="s-content__primary">

                    <h1 class="s-content__title">Learn More About Us</h1>

                    <p class="lead">Welcome to Gamma Game Hub! This project is dedicated to those who love playing and exploring all kinds of games. We consider our site a safe space for the gaming community to share their thoughts with each other and with us. Gamma Game Hub is also the perfect platform for game creators. Companies and new developers are always welcome to contact us and feature their games on our page.</p>

                    <p>At Gamma Game Hub, we want everyone, from casual players to hardcore enthusiasts, to feel like they belong. Join discussions, find new games, and connect with other gamers who love what you love. We're here to make gaming more than just a hobby – it's a shared experience.</p>

                    <hr>

                    <div class="row block-large-1-2 block-tab-full s-content__blocks">
                        <div class="column">
                            <h4>Who</h4>
                            <p>Meet the passionate individuals behind Gamma Game Hub, each dedicated to fostering a vibrant gaming community. Our team believes in creating a space where people can freely express their love for games without limitations. With diverse backgrounds and unique perspectives, each member contributes to making Gamma Game Hub a hub of creativity and excitement.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="column">
                            <h4>When</h4>
                            <p>Stay tuned for thrilling events and gaming sessions hosted by Gamma Game Hub. We regularly organize gatherings, tournaments, and special releases, providing opportunities for gamers to come together and celebrate their shared passion for gaming.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="column">
                            <h4>What</h4>
                            <p>Dive into a diverse range of games featured on Gamma Game Hub. From the latest releases to hidden gems, our platform is a curated collection catering to the varied tastes of our gaming community. Explore in-depth reviews, insightful articles, and engaging content that goes beyond the surface of gaming.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="column">
                            <h4>How</h4>
                            <p>Gamma Game Hub is designed with user-friendly interfaces and features, ensuring seamless navigation on our platform. Connect with fellow gamers through our forums, share your experiences, and stay updated on the latest gaming trends. Whether you're a seasoned player or just starting, our platform provides the tools and resources to enhance your gaming journey.</p>
                        </div>

                    </div>

                </div> <!-- end s-content__primary -->

            </section>

        </div> <!-- end column -->
    </div> <!-- end row -->
</section> <!-- end s-content -->
